thread.title: Saudi- Jarir Marketing Q2 profit rises 14.6
thread.title_full: Saudi- Jarir Marketing Q2 profit rises 14.6 | MENAFN.COM

author: Arab News
title: Saudi- Jarir Marketing Q2 profit rises 14.6
text:
(MENAFN - Arab News) JEDDAH: Jarir Marketing Saudi Arabia's second-largest retailer reported a 14.6 percent rise in second-quarter net profit. 
The company made a net profit of SR154.9 million (41.30 million) in the three months ending June 30 compared with SR135.2 million a year earlier it said in a statement. 
Seven analysts polled by Reuters had forecast on average a quarterly net profit of SR158.7 million.
